
Basic Build
------------------

It can be built with autotools, cmake, or meson

1) autotools
autoreconf -fi
./configure
make
# make install

2) cmake
cmake -B _build -S $(pwd)
cmake --build _build
# cmake --install _build

3) meson
meson setup _build
meson compile -C _build    #meson<0.55: ninja -C _build
# meson install -C _build


Packaging
------------------

Template samples are located in 'package-templates/'

